6:
Wh-what am I supposed to be
looking for when treating sprites and
mushrooms?!
11:
Organic flesh and machine parts
can be combined like this?!
16:
Their whole bodies are made of
metal?!
25:
I was told to see the world... But this
is too much! How am I supposed to
treat such a wide variety of people?!
29:
She gets like this every time we go
out to another world...
32:
What're you so panicked about? It's
not like you NEED to be helping
people outside your area of
expertise.
36:
I mean, I guess? Sure, I only treated
beastfolk and humans back home,
and I've never seen so much metal
in a body before...
40:
But as part of the Fellowship of Floof,
I need to be able to treat anyone
and everyone, no matter what world
I'm in.
44:
That's the kind of attitude I need to
have if I want to be like the rest of
the crew. They're always healing
people up right away!
49:
Is that the kind of nurse you want to
be?
64:
We got a message from your vice
captain!
68:
The doctor from your hometown
collapsed in the middle of workâ€”
76:
You dummy! How could you strain
your back like that?!
79:
Ahaha... This is why I asked the
others not to tell you...
82:
Everyone on this Float was real
worried about you, you know. Talk
about being popular.
84:
Haha, it's more like... I'm the only
doctor on this small Float, so it's no
wonder they're worried.
85:
There's a lot of old folk here for me
to take care of, but I put myself out
of commission... I feel terrible.
88:
In that case, I'll look after them
instead. At least until you're back on
your feet.
91:
I can handle it. I'm a member of the
Fellowship of Floof, after all.
95:
Plus I did all that training after going
to Starview. I KNOW I can do this...
99: But not alone, right? We'll help.
104:
Can't have you straining your back
too. Just tell us what to do.
114:
...I can't believe I almost ran off on
my own.
116:
That would've been a huge mistake.
I guess I haven't learned my lesson
yet.
127:
Thank goodness we had you,
Pythica! You looked after us real
good, even without the doc around!
130:
Ehehe, you think so? I guess
something like this...
133:
...I couldn't have done on my own. It's
only thanks to Alk and the others
being here too that I managed it.
136:
Ehehe, maybe one day soon I can
stand on my own two feet.
145:
The most important thing is that
everyone here is healthy and happy.
148:
I'll get to my goal one day, one step
at a time! I just have to focus on
doing everything I can in the
moment...
154:
That attitude is exactly why we all
support you.
156:
Be proud, Pythica. You're already a
wonderful nurse.
160:
I was too anxious to see progress,
huh...
163:
I looked up to the Fellowship of Floof
ever since they saved our Float from
pirates.
166:
They healed everyone, including the
pirates! I'll never forget how much of
a difference they made.
168:
...I wanted to be medical pro like
them.
172:
But I lost sight of WHY I did. Today
reminded me that what matters
most is helping those in need!
175:
Can I count on you to give me a
hand whenever duty calls?
179: Do you even need to ask?
184:
...Anything is possible so long as we
work together.
186: I'm proud that you realized that.
196: You are an amazing nurse, Pythica.
201:
Thanks, Stella! You're so kind and
cute and ohhh! I love you too!
205:
Yeah... I've gotta work even harder,
so you guys can rely on me back!
208:
We'll make everyone out there
happy and healthy, or my name isn't
Pythica, proud Fellowship of Floof
nurse!
